high_descs: walk to face counter between fridge and stove
pick up the apple from the counter top
chill apple in fridge, remove apple from fridge
anns.task_desc: put a chilled apple into a microwave

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the counter.
Pick up the apple from the right side of the counter.
Hold the apple and take a few steps left, to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the apple inside. Shut the door and then open it again. Take out the apple and shut the door.
Hold the apple and turn around to the sink. Look above the sink.
Open the microwave and place the apple inside, shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Chill an apple and place it in a microwave

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen counter on your right.
Grab an apple from the counter.
Go to the fridge on the left.
Put the apple in the fridge, then take it out.
Walk to the kitchen sink behind you.
Put the apple in the microwave above the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill an apple and heat it.
